    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Validation results at all five operating points satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion with normalized error below 6.5%. An uncertainty quantification campaign was conducted and results are discussed in the validation report; the hemolysis index rank ordering is confirmed robust. The model is credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device as described in the COU.",
